	<s:slide id="what_is_p2p">
		<s:title>What is P2P</s:title>
		<s:content>
<p>
No clear definition, but ...<br />
<ol>
  <li>Peer nodes know about other peers</li>
  <li>Peers form virtual network</li>
  <li>Peers are grouped into peergroups</li>
  <li>Peers are Server and Client</li>
</ol>
</p>
		</s:content>
	</s:slide>


